favoritelistfor: (for user) string displayed under the special page title
nofavoritelist: Displayed on the special page and embedded favorites lists when the favorites list is empty
favoritelistanontext: Displayed on the special page and embedded favorites lists to anonymous users
favoritenologin: Title of the special page displayed to anonymous users
addedfavoritetext: Tooltip displayed when a page is added to a user's favorites via the star
removedfavoritetext: Tooltip displayed when a page is removed from a user's favorites via the star
favorite: Text displayed in the page menu to favorite a page
unfavorite: Text displayed in the page menu to remove a page from a user's favorites
favoriteerrortext: Displayed when an error occurs while toggling a favorite
unfavoriteing: Displayed in the page menu while removing a page from the user's favorites
favoriteing: Displayed in the page menu while adding a page from the user's favorites
tooltip-ca-favorite: Tooltip displayed on the Favorite link and the star on a page not in the user's favorites
tooltip-ca-unfavorite: Tooltip displayed on the Unfavorite link and the star on a page in the user's favorites
favoritelistedit-numitems: Displayed on the favorites edit page when there is at least one page in the user's favorites
favoritelistedit-noitems: Displayed on the favorites edit page when there are no pages in the user's favorites
favoritelistedit-normal-title: Title displayed on the edit favorites page
favoritelistedit-normal-legend: Form title displayed on the edit favorites page
favoritelistedit-normal-explain: Text in the remove favorites form
favoritelistedit-normal-submit: Text displayed on the edit favorites submit button
favoritelistedit-raw-title: Title displayed on the edit raw favorites list page
favoritelistedit-raw-legend: Form title displayed on the edit raw favorites list page
favoritelistedit-raw-explain: Text in the edit raw favorites form
favoritelistedit-raw-titles: Text displayed immediately before the raw favorites list
favoritelistedit-raw-submit: Text displayed on the edit raw favorites submit button
favoritelistedit-raw-done: Text displayed after editing the raw favorites list
favoritelistedit-raw-added: Text displayed after editing the raw favorites list indicating what favorites were added
favoritelistedit-raw-removed: Text displayed after editing the raw favorites list indicating what favorites were removed
favoritelisttools-view: View favorites page listing on favorites special pages
favoritelisttools-edit: View and edit favorites page listing on favorites special pages
favoritelisttools-raw: Edit raw favorites list page listing on favorites special pages
api-error-favorites-not-logged-in: Error message returned by the API when an anonymous user tries to use the favorites API module
